{"id":91532,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/08/隐藏在你家里的恐怖杀手/","date":"2010-08-05T20:35:11Z","modified":"2010-08-05T20:35:11Z","title":"隐藏在你家里的恐怖杀手","content":"<p><p>来自: <a href=\"http://www.feedzshare.com/b/931251/2\">www.yeeyan.org &#8211; FeedzShare</a>  <br />\n<br />发布时间:2010年08月04日,  已有 5 人推荐 </p>\n<hr>\n<div>\n<p>原作者：<br />来源<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sciencetech/article-1299938/Extreme-close-ups-creepy-crawlies-infest-homes.html\">Extreme close-ups of the creepy crawlies that infest our homes  | Mail Online</a><br />译者<a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/95021\">WideBridge</a></p>\n<p>这些家伙乍看起来很像好莱坞大片中的星外来客，其实它们已经入侵到你的家中。这些面目狰狞的家伙是经过放大100万倍的螨虫、苍蝇和跳蚤，它们就隐藏我们的地毯、窗帘、沙发和厨房的角落里，以食物碎屑为生。<br />  <img height=\"397\" alt=\"Itchy feeling: This image taken through a Scanning Electron Micrograph shows a house dust mite, which lives on shed skin cells\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/08/03/article-1299938-0AAB7583000005DC-377_634x397.jpg\" width=\"634\" /></p>\n<p>这是看了令人浑身发痒的尘螨，它们以人的皮肤碎屑为生</p>\n<p><img height=\"636\" alt=\"Feline friend: This image shows a cat flea in its favourite habitat and is magnified more than 100 times\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/08/03/article-1299938-0AAB749C000005DC-287_634x636.jpg\" width=\"634\" /></p>\n<p>这是与猫相依为命的虱子，已经放大了100倍</p>\n<p><img height=\"636\" alt=\"Making a buzz: A super close-up of a common housefly reveals the tiny hairs across its entire body\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/08/03/article-1299938-0AAB7488000005DC-905_634x636.jpg\" width=\"634\" /></p>\n<p>这是特写镜头下的家蝇，浑身上下有一层绒毛，能携带大量病菌</p>\n<p><img height=\"587\" alt=\"Hideous: A close-up of the head of a bluebottle fly larva, with its mouth on the right\" src=\"http://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2010/08/03/article-1299938-0AAB7470000005DC-411_634x587.jpg\" width=\"634\" /></p>\n<p>这是绿头苍蝇幼虫的头部特写，口器长在右侧</p>\n<p><img height=\"458\" alt=\"Cereal killer: This red flour beetle inhabits the kitchen and likes to eat cornflakes, 